  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/ad772c99f184787b88ca0a675d3fa734.avif?t=1744136585\" width=614 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Condemned to purge your death sentence, you and a group of fellow inmates are sent to Earth—a cursed, abandoned wasteland. Teleport to a location of your choice, scavenge for tools, and outlast the competition to earn your freedom. Manage your oxygen carefully, use every resource at your disposal, and, above all, avoid the curse that haunts the planet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/637a46b448bc520f3410f1d7b800c011.poster.avif?t=1744136585\" width=570 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/637a46b448bc520f3410f1d7b800c011.webm?t=1744136585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/637a46b448bc520f3410f1d7b800c011.mp4?t=1744136585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/9f510bc2103f442a2587560fc08ecd14.avif?t=1744136585\" width=614 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Marked by the curse, your mission is clear: pass it on before it consumes your soul. As the hunter, you must target one of your fellow inmates. Deceive them with lies, lure them into traps, or pursue them in a relentless chase. The curse grants you supernatural powers—soar through the air with powerful leaps, track others through walls, and hear their pounding heartbeats. But beware: the longer you remain cursed, the closer you edge toward oblivion.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/5da92565858215b75d77e7f3fae8c5dc.poster.avif?t=1744136585\" width=570 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/5da92565858215b75d77e7f3fae8c5dc.webm?t=1744136585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/5da92565858215b75d77e7f3fae8c5dc.mp4?t=1744136585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/c240163b0b097e7d4a87adebc3ff5443.avif?t=1744136585\" width=614 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death is only the beginning. Consumed by the curse, your soul transforms into one of many ghastly ghouls, each designed to haunt the living. Crawl, fly, or sprint—every ghoul offers unique abilities to navigate the terrain and hunt the remaining prisoners. Master each form’s strengths, exploit their weaknesses, and join forces with the cursed to spread chaos and dread among the survivors.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/2d0a90d8d3939f2d499925af17064e3f.poster.avif?t=1744136585\" width=570 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/2d0a90d8d3939f2d499925af17064e3f.webm?t=1744136585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/2d0a90d8d3939f2d499925af17064e3f.mp4?t=1744136585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/ad772c99f184787b88ca0a675d3fa734.avif?t=1744136585\" width=614 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Condemned to purge your death sentence, you and a group of fellow inmates are sent to Earth—a cursed, abandoned wasteland. Teleport to a location of your choice, scavenge for tools, and outlast the competition to earn your freedom. Manage your oxygen carefully, use every resource at your disposal, and, above all, avoid the curse that haunts the planet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/637a46b448bc520f3410f1d7b800c011.poster.avif?t=1744136585\" width=570 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/637a46b448bc520f3410f1d7b800c011.webm?t=1744136585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/637a46b448bc520f3410f1d7b800c011.mp4?t=1744136585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/9f510bc2103f442a2587560fc08ecd14.avif?t=1744136585\" width=614 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Marked by the curse, your mission is clear: pass it on before it consumes your soul. As the hunter, you must target one of your fellow inmates. Deceive them with lies, lure them into traps, or pursue them in a relentless chase. The curse grants you supernatural powers—soar through the air with powerful leaps, track others through walls, and hear their pounding heartbeats. But beware: the longer you remain cursed, the closer you edge toward oblivion.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/5da92565858215b75d77e7f3fae8c5dc.poster.avif?t=1744136585\" width=570 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/5da92565858215b75d77e7f3fae8c5dc.webm?t=1744136585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/5da92565858215b75d77e7f3fae8c5dc.mp4?t=1744136585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/c240163b0b097e7d4a87adebc3ff5443.avif?t=1744136585\" width=614 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death is only the beginning. Consumed by the curse, your soul transforms into one of many ghastly ghouls, each designed to haunt the living. Crawl, fly, or sprint—every ghoul offers unique abilities to navigate the terrain and hunt the remaining prisoners. Master each form’s strengths, exploit their weaknesses, and join forces with the cursed to spread chaos and dread among the survivors.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/2d0a90d8d3939f2d499925af17064e3f.poster.avif?t=1744136585\" width=570 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/2d0a90d8d3939f2d499925af17064e3f.webm?t=1744136585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/2d0a90d8d3939f2d499925af17064e3f.mp4?t=1744136585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
